								li
									span.icon.hotel-icon-05
									span 2 Bedrooms
								li
									span.icon.mdi.mdi-vector-square
									span 480 Sq Ft
								li
									span.icon.hotel-icon-26
									span 1 Garage
						.features-block-item
							a.link.link-1(href='#')
								span.icon.mdi.mdi-heart-outline
								| Add to Favorites

					p Choose this property if you are looking for a modern house near the ocean shore. With 2 bathrooms and 2 bedrooms as well as a single garage, it is a perfect option for a small family.
					p This home has been completely renovated within the past year and features amazing views and sunsets of the local lake, solid wood cabinets (and loads of them), granite counters with colored glass backsplash,  sliding glass doors across the entire family room allowing beautiful views of the lake etc. Its affordable price serves as a great bonus for a family looking for an opportunity to save money on Miami real estate.

					// Bootstrap collapse
					#accordion1.card-group-custom.card-group-corporate(
					role='tablist'
					aria-multiselectable='false')
						+card({
							show: true,
							parentId: 'accordion1',
							number: '1',
							header: 'Address'
